  {"zh":"[Concession] 讓步承認","en":"Admittedly, / It must be acknowledged that","note":"Admittedly 是 CLB 9 讓步詞首選，比 However 更誠懇","category":"peel","distractors":["But we must admit","However it is true","Although we know"]},
